":"海林Lin","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1917715,"ip_address":"","ucode":"26333AE3DFAF9D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/43/13/649ccaa9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1628474254,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"110878","content":"你可以把拉普拉斯分布理解成对称的幂率分布。","user_name":"作者回复","comment_id":306254,"uid":"1045807","ip_address":"","utype":1,"ctime":1628511558,"user_name_real":"郭大侠"}],"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"18808343438","product_id":100084801,"comment_content":"拉普拉斯分布和幂律分布的区别是什么呢？","like_count":4,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2727690,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/29/9f/0a/51a9c792.jpg","nickname":"艺霖子","note":"","ucode":"6451E7DCAC2A63","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":388547,"discussion_content":"幂律分布是老师在第三讲中的内容。幂律分布就是从直方图中体现出来呈指数下降或者上升的分布形式。帕累托法则背后的规律就是幂律分布。\n拉普拉斯分布，从图来看，像凸形塔尖曲线，向下呈内凹金字塔状。\n把拉普拉斯比作一座山，那么幂律分布就是山的一半，从中间劈开。\n幂律分布的意义是告诉我们，不要把所有的事情都放在最重要的优先级上，遵循二八定律。\n拉普拉斯分布告诉我们，当我们要决定是否做一件事的时候，先对其进行分析，那你要分析，你的根据是什么，根据市场实际情况，准确分析趋势，也就是大势，选择你想要的模型，为你的决定做出有理有据的信息。\n所以意义不同，根据你想要干啥。\n同学，这是我的理解，只能帮你到这了。\n","likes_number":5,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1628829522,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1045807,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/f5/2f/138174f7.jpg","nickname":"郭大侠","note":"","ucode":"52D11F3D6C29E8","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":524685,"discussion_content":"你可以把拉普拉斯分布理解成对称的幂率分布。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1628511558,"is_liked":false,"can_